replies.bodyText:
@rnveach, sorry for late reply, I got disconnected with my own code.
It is for the case when lcurly is on new line, then curlies should be indented on braceAdjustment value ahead of the base.
It is for old style java codes.
class A 
  { // braceAdj
      void main() {} // braceAdj + basicOffset
  }  

class A {
    void main() {} //  basicOffset
}  

